<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>NAIH CHIN CH361</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Na kan kawh thawng kha Bawipa ka theih cang, Na kan dawtnak a ka
 chimh, Zumhnak in na sinah kai chin ka duh Na ke hram ah um ka duh.

[C1]
   Jesuh a in vai-lamtahnak kha, Keimah kha ka naihter tuah, Naih chin,
   naih chin, naih chin, naih chin ka Bawipa; Naih chinter nangmah sinah.

[V2]
 Pathian na riantuan awkah ka thleidang, Nangmah min in tuah ka duh,
 Keimah ka thlarau ruahchannak hmu seh, Kei ca nangmah nawl siseh.

[C2]
   Jesuh a in vai-lamtahnak kha, Keimah kha ka naihter tuah, Naih chin,
   naih chin, naih chin, naih chin ka Bawipa; Naih chinter nangmah sinah.

[V3]
 Nangmah ke hram ah thla ka cam tikah, Lawmhnak zeitluk in ka hmuh, Kan
 dawi dua cio bantukin kan in nawl Na ka chawnh ahcun ka duh.

[C3]
   Jesuh a in vai-lamtahnak kha, Keimah kha ka naihter tuah, Naih chin,
   naih chin, naih chin, naih chin ka Bawipa; Naih chinter nangmah sinah.

[V4]
 A sungmi dawtnak, keimah ka hngal lo, Thihnak tiva tan hlanah,
 Lawmhnak bik kha keimah nih ka hmuh lai, Thluachuahnak ka hmuh tikah.

[C4]
   Jesuh a in vai-lamtahnak kha, Keimah kha ka naihter tuah, Naih chin,
   naih chin, naih chin, naih chin ka Bawipa; Naih chinter nangmah sinah.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
<hymn_number>361</hymn_number>
</song>